		"description": "<p dir=\"ltr\">Beginning at 6th level, you may use your magic to temporarily improve your @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.vbrdlgurs5vnqgki]{Undead Servant}, giving it one of the following upgrades at the cost specified. These upgrades require an action to activate, and last until you complete a long rest. You may not use the same upgrade more than once per long rest, but you may have multiple upgrades active at a time.</p>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">Magical Fortitude</h2>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">You may use a spell slot to give your Undead Servant the ability to reroll one failed saving throw of your choice.</p>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">Unnatural Defence</h2>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">If you use a spell slot while you have a prepared spell from the p<em>rotection&nbsp;</em>school, your Undead Servant increases its AC by a number equal to the level of the spell slot used.</p>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">Necrotic Power</h2>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">If you use a spell slot while you have a prepared spell from the n<em>ecrotic&nbsp;</em>school, your Undead Servant deals an extra 1d4 + the spell slot level necrotic damage.&nbsp;</p>",
